---
import Youtube from "../../components/youtube.astro";
---

<section class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-4 pt-16 md:pt-24">
  <h2 class="h2 text-primary-800 text-center">Student Stories and Resources</h2>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-16">
    <article class="relative bg-tertiary-600 text-white p-8 pt-16">
      <span
        aria-hidden="true"
        class="top-0 left-1/2 absolute -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/3 lg:-translate-y-1/2 bg-white rounded-full p-4 border-4 border-tertiary-600"
      >
        <img src="/icons/messages-question.svg" alt="" class="max-w-10" />
      </span>
      <h3 class="text-tertiary-300 font-bold uppercase h4 mb-2">FAFSA</h3>
      <p class="font-bold uppercase h4 mb-2">Applying for financial aid?</p>
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm">
        The U.S. Department of Education recently changed the Free Application for Federal Student
        Aid (FAFSA). Check out Messiah's FAFSA changes webpage for details and watch this video
        series to learn more.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://www.messiah.edu/homepage/5160/2024-25_fafsa_changes"
        class="btn btn-secondary text-primary-800 w-full mb-2">Messiah's FAFSA changes</a
      >
      <a
        href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLtr3wy4M_CJ2Hrd0UwCAWJOgOPu8l_ZLf"
        class="btn btn-secondary text-primary-800 w-full">FAFSA video series</a
      >
    </article>
    <article class="relative bg-primary-800 text-white p-8 pt-16">
      <span
        aria-hidden="true"
        class="top-0 left-1/2 absolute -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/3 lg:-translate-y-1/2 bg-white rounded-full p-4 border-4 border-primary-800"
      >
        <img src="/icons/introduction.svg" alt="" class="max-w-10" />
      </span>
      <h3 class="text-tertiary-300 font-bold uppercase h4 mb-2">What students are saying</h3>
      <blockquote>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm before:content-['“'] after:content-['”']">
          Messiah is worth the investment of my time and resources because it provides an education
          that lasts for a lifetime through excellent teaching and persistent care for the
          well-being and overall success of each student.
        </p>

        <cite class="font-bold uppercase not-italic text-sm">Abigail Chang '24</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </article>
    <article class="relative bg-tertiary-600 text-white p-8 pt-16">
      <span
        aria-hidden="true"
        class="top-0 left-1/2 absolute -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/3 lg:-translate-y-1/2 bg-white rounded-full p-4 border-4 border-tertiary-600"
      >
        <img src="/icons/tv-retro.svg" alt="" class="max-w-10" />
      </span>
      <h3 class="text-tertiary-300 font-bold uppercase h4 mb-2">Watch</h3>
      <p class="font-bold uppercase h4 mb-2">Hear from our students</p>
      <Youtube videoId="U8QiaTyA08M" />
    </article>
    <article class="relative bg-primary-800 text-white p-8 pt-16">
      <span
        aria-hidden="true"
        class="top-0 left-1/2 absolute -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/3 lg:-translate-y-1/2 bg-white rounded-full p-4 border-4 border-primary-800"
      >
        <img src="/icons/family.svg" alt="" class="max-w-10" />
      </span>
      <h3 class="text-tertiary-300 font-bold uppercase h4 mb-2">What parents are saying</h3>
      <blockquote>
        <p class="mb-4 before:content-['“'] after:content-['”'] text-sm">
          The high quality of education and strong Christian stance, which Messiah holds to, were
          reasons that inspired our daughter to select this outstanding college. The opportunity to
          attend Messiah was made possible financially by campus scholarships that eased the burden
          of private college tuition.
        </p>

        <cite class="font-bold uppercase not-italic text-sm"
          >Lloyd and Kathy Myhre, parents of a Messiah graduate</cite
        >
      </blockquote>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
